readme:
Service Usage

This service is used by CSP to retrieve the Integrity Status of an Agent from GOIS and then displays. CSP provides hyperlink to GOIS using GOIS Client ID.

Service Behaviour

CSP retrieves data from GOIS. CSP displays data with hyperlink to GOIS using the GOISCLIENTID.
